do anything else. Dad.

1125
01:10:11.781 --> 01:10:14.700
- I've been down this road before.

1126
01:10:14.701 --> 01:10:18.647
It always ends up in the same
place. a big pile of shit.

1127
01:10:18.648 --> 01:10:20.565
Do something else. Art.

1128
01:10:23.461 --> 01:10:25.628
(beeping)

1129
01:10:32.075 --> 01:10:34.629
