1132
01:10:41.981 --> 01:10:44.140
If I don't follow my heart right now

1133
01:10:44.141 --> 01:10:45.207
what would I have to loop back on

1134
01:10:45.208 --> 01:10:48.125
and cherish when I'm 100 years old?

1135
01:10:49.795 --> 01:10:51.992
- If your music is gonna pay for this

1136
01:10:51.993 --> 01:10:54.207
them I am not gonna have the surgery.

1137
01:10:54.208 --> 01:10:55.041
- Dad.

1138
01:10:56.088 --> 01:10:57.921
- It's my choice. Art.

1139
01:10:58.807 --> 01:11:00.807
I hope you can respect that.

1140
01:11:01.781 --> 01:11:02.614
- But.

1141
01:11:07.981 --> 01:11:11.511
You know what? Congratulations. Dad.

1142
01:11:11.512 --> 01:11:12.679
You win again.

