- Yeah.

1186
01:13:45.361 --> 01:13:46.360
- [Caroline] Arthur.

1187
01:13:46.361 --> 01:13:47.279
- Caroline.

1188
01:13:47.280 --> 01:13:48.547
(laughing)

1189
01:13:48.548 --> 01:13:50.733
- Hey. hey. how are you guys?

1190
01:13:50.734 --> 01:13:51.587
- Lavanya.

1191
01:13:51.588 --> 01:13:52.420
- Yes. right.

1192
01:13:52.421 --> 01:13:54.002
- Yes. thanks.

1193
01:13:54.003 --> 01:13:55.211
- Congrats on the song. man.

1194
01:13:55.212 --> 01:13:56.053
- Thank you.

1195
01:13:56.054 --> 01:13:58.747
- You sound so damn
different than you used to.

1196
01:13:58.748 --> 01:14:02.959
- Yeah. that's funny
how that happens. right?

1197
01:14:02.960 --> 01:14:05.640
- Look who we have here today. people.

1198
01:14:05.641 --> 01:14:07.985
Arthur Holzenberg. huh?

1199
01:14:07.986 --> 01:14:09.293
(clapping)

1200
01:14:09.294 --> 01:14:10.707
(laughing)

1201
01:14:10.708 --> 01:14:12.800
Come on. sing a song for us.

1202
01:14:12.801 --> 01:14:13.827
- Maybe another time. okay?

1203
01:14:13.828 --> 01:14:14.660
- [Caroline] Come on.

1204
01:14:14.661 --> 01:14:15.640
- [Lavanya] He's a little tired.

1205
01:14:15.641 --> 01:14:17.760
- No. no. no. no. no. no.

1206
01:14:17.761 --> 01:14:18.594
Sing.

1207
01:14:19.654 --> 01:14:20.487
Sing.

1208
01:14:21.467 --> 01:14:22.300
Sing.

1209
01:14:23.240 --> 01:14:24.747
- [Crowd] Sing!

1210
01:14:24.748 --> 01:14:26.133
Sing!

1211
01:14:26.134 --> 01:14:27.467
Sing!

1212
01:14:27.468 --> 01:14:28.827
Sing!

1213
01:14:28.828 --> 01:14:30.093
Sing!

1214
01:14:30.094 --> 01:14:31.386
Sing!

1215
01:14:31.387 --> 01:14:32.785
Sing!

1216
01:14:32.786 --> 01:14:35.826
- [Caroline] Yeah! All right!

1217
01:14:35.827 --> 01:14:37.488
(laughing)

1218
01:14:37.489 --> 01:14:38.321
- [Crowd] Woo!

1219
01:14:38.322 --> 01:14:40.905
Woo!
(clapping)

1220
01:14:51.344 --> 01:14:54.177
(breathing heavy)

1221
01:15:02.160 --> 01:15:05.439
- Let's get a drink of water or something.

1222
01:15:05.440 --> 01:15:08.273
(breathing heavy)

1223
01:15:36.783 --> 01:15:38.919
(mellow music)

1224
01:15:38.920 --> 01:15:41.587
(water running)

1225
01:16:06.361 --> 01:16:09.111
(dramatic music)

1226
01:17:06.643 --> 01:17:09.722
- If you think I enjoy coming down here.

1227
01:17:09.723 --> 01:17:12.188
you got another thing coming.

1228
01:17:12.189 --> 01:17:13.456
(laughs)

1229
01:17:13.457 --> 01:17:14.776
How you doing. buddy?

1230
01:17:14.777 --> 01:17:17.277
- Yeah. I'm doing great. Adam.

1231
01:17:18.470 --> 01:17:21.256
- I got some good news for you.

1232
01:17:21.257 --> 01:17:23.696
They found you a liver.

1233
