- You know. my friend.
sometime you're just too much.

1238
01:17:50.912 --> 01:17:52.971
Well. think about it.

1239
01:17:52.972 --> 01:17:54.498
- Take it with ya.

1240
01:17:54.499 --> 01:17:55.538
- [Adam] Think about it.

1241
01:17:55.539 --> 01:17:56.563
- Take it.

1242
01:17:56.564 --> 01:17:58.151
- Think about it.

1243
01:17:58.152 --> 01:17:59.569
- Piss off. Adam.

1244
01:18:00.952 --> 01:18:02.952
Get the fuck outta here.

1245
01:18:17.419 --> 01:18:19.218
(knocking)

1246
01:18:19.219 --> 01:18:20.552
- [Adam] Arthur!

1247
01:18:21.511 --> 01:18:23.297
(knocking)

1248
01:18:23.298 --> 01:18:24.245
Arthur!

1249
01:18:24.246 --> 01:18:26.338
(knocking)

1250
01:18:26.339 --> 01:18:27.171
- All right. all right!

1251
01:18:27.172 --> 01:18:28.379
- [Adam] Arthur!

1252
01:18:28.380 --> 01:18:29.523
Open the door.

1253
01:18:29.524 --> 01:18:31.029
- Coming.

1254
01:18:31.030 --> 01:18:31.863
Jesus.

1255
01:18:33.937 --> 01:18:35.881
- Come on. what are
you doing in this mess?

1256
01:18:35.882 --> 01:18:37.549
- Yeah. man. do you.

1257
01:18:38.644 --> 01:18:40.416
you don't have any blow on ya. do ya?

1258
01:18:40.417 --> 01:18:41.309
- Arthur.

1259
01:18:41.310 --> 01:18:44.562
- Come on. man. I'm celebrating.

1260
01:18:44.563 --> 01:18:45.443
I'm enjoying my life.

1261
01:18:45.444 --> 01:18:47.536
