1262
01:18:47.537 --> 01:18:48.370
- Yeah.

1263
01:18:49.404 --> 01:18:51.213
You've clearly gone crazy.

1264
01:18:51.214 --> 01:18:52.381
- Yes. I have!

1265
01:18:53.964 --> 01:18:56.214
Y'all play out lately? Huh?

1266
01:18:58.097 --> 01:18:59.347
What about you?

1267
01:19:00.190 --> 01:19:04.349
Ringo Starr over here. Keeping it tight?

1268
01:19:04.350 --> 01:19:05.856
What about you?

1269
01:19:05.857 --> 01:19:10.309
See. see. you can all
perform whenever you want.

1270
01:19:10.310 --> 01:19:12.668
I can't do that anymore.

1271
01:19:12.669 --> 01:19:13.789
