1275
01:19:27.322 --> 01:19:29.109
If your music's what's gonna pay for this

1276
01:19:29.110 --> 01:19:31.610
then I don't want the surgery.

1277
01:19:33.084 --> 01:19:36.917
That's was before I
could tell him the truth.

1278
01:19:39.337 --> 01:19:40.441
I couldn't tell him.

1279
01:19:40.442 --> 01:19:41.274
- Why not?

1280
01:19:41.275 --> 01:19:43.216
- Because how do you follow that. La?

1281
01:19:43.217 --> 01:19:46.295
Hey dad. I stole your work

1282
01:19:46.296 --> 01:19:49.213
and sold it to the world as my own.

1283
01:19:51.764 --> 01:19:54.136
It's actually pretty funny.

1284
01:19:54.137 --> 01:19:57.163
I mean he never wanted me
to sing in the first place.

1285
01:19:57.164 --> 01:19:59.216
and here I am unable to sing.

1286
01:19:59.217 --> 01:20:02.029
So let's celebrate that. huh?

1287
01:20:02.030 --> 01:20:02.863
- Arthur.

1288
01:20:03.844 --> 01:20:08.361
What we did. we did for Harry.

1289
01:20:09.268 --> 01:20:12.927
And that sacrifice ain’t for nothing.

1290
01:20:12.928 --> 01:20:15.595
FYI. they found him a new liver.

1291
01:20:16.671 --> 01:20:19.588
but he's still refusing to consent.

1292
01:20:21.499 --> 01:20:22.832
- Hey. look man.

1293
01:20:25.538 --> 01:20:27.978
I didn't know I'd give
a damn about any of this

1294
01:20:27.979 --> 01:20:30.524
when I first saw you in that bar.

1295
01:20:30.525 --> 01:20:32.324
You're a good dude.

1296
01:20:32.325 --> 01:20:35.492
But if you give up on your own family.

1297
01:20:38.090 --> 01:20:41.257
you'll have nothing left to live for.

1298
01:20:43.043 --> 01:20:43.876
- Hey.

1299
01:20:44.912 --> 01:20:47.293
We're not going to give up on you.

1300
01:20:47.294 --> 01:20:50.977
So you can't give up on your father.

1301
01:20:50.978 --> 01:20:51.811
Okay?

