1303
01:21:06.285 --> 01:21:07.431
Hi. sir.

1304
01:21:07.432 --> 01:21:08.432
I'm Lavanya.

1305
01:21:11.339 --> 01:21:12.496
- Hello. sir.

1306
01:21:12.497 --> 01:21:13.330
Will Goff.

1307
01:21:14.792 --> 01:21:15.625
Big fan.

1308
01:21:18.991 --> 01:21:19.823
- What is all this?

1309
01:21:19.824 --> 01:21:21.824
