thought process here. Dad.

1316
01:21:38.111 --> 01:21:40.111
because clearly I don't.

1317
01:21:43.632 --> 01:21:45.444
And I don't think this
decision that you're making

1318
01:21:45.445 --> 01:21:47.804
is in anyone's best interest.

1319
01:21:47.805 --> 01:21:49.591
I don't understand why
it's so hard for you

1320
01:21:49.592 --> 01:21:52.538
