The only person from stopping
you from getting this is you.

1325
01:22:08.579 --> 01:22:09.951
- Can I speak now?

1326
01:22:09.952 --> 01:22:14.884
- After everyone in this room
says what they came to say.

1327
01:22:14.885 --> 01:22:15.718
La?

1328
01:22:17.339 --> 01:22:20.085
- Sir. I've known Arthur
for a long time now.

1329
01:22:21.360 --> 01:22:23.527
And I've got a father too.

1330
01:22:26.209 --> 01:22:28.471
- It's all right. go on.

1331
01:22:28.472 --> 01:22:29.815
- No child would wanna see their father

1332
01:22:29.816 --> 01:22:32.399
go through something like this.

1333
01:22:34.377 --> 01:22:35.209
- Will.

1334
01:22:35.210 --> 01:22:36.042
- Hm?

1335
01:22:36.043 --> 01:22:36.895
Do you want me to?

1336
01:22:36.896 --> 01:22:37.729
- Yeah.

1337
01:22:39.311 --> 01:22:40.144
Go head.

