01:22:43.352 --> 01:22:45.444
- Arthur is a good man.

1339
01:22:45.445 --> 01:22:48.695
And I think you should consider surgery

1340
01:22:50.713 --> 01:22:55.309
because whatever he had
done. he's done for you.

1341
01:22:55.310 --> 01:22:59.789
- If you don't sign the
consent form today. Harold.

1342
01:22:59.790 --> 01:23:02.232
