1364
01:24:29.094 --> 01:24:30.011
You see me?

1365
01:24:32.043 --> 01:24:34.002
I don't have any reason for hanging around

1366
01:24:34.003 --> 01:24:37.836
to see him go down the
same shitty road. Adam.

1367
01:24:38.897 --> 01:24:39.730
- For me?

1368
01:24:41.203 --> 01:24:43.286
Just fucking die already.

1369
01:24:50.424 --> 01:24:52.257
- He ain’t you. Harold.

1370
