1466
01:32:24.348 --> 01:32:25.548
(laughing)

1467
01:32:25.549 --> 01:32:27.815
- Shit out of here. man.
that's a good start.

1468
01:32:27.816 --> 01:32:28.648
- And you know what?

1469
01:32:28.649 --> 01:32:31.720
When you get out of here
and you get all better.

1470
01:32:31.721 --> 01:32:33.479
I wanna take you somewhere.

